GARNET EQUITY CAPITAL HOLDINGS AUM, Portfolio Value and Historical 13F
Garnet Equity Capital Holdings Inc had $189.98 million assets under management as of Monday, March 31, 2014. The historical portfolio values of the hedge fund were: 
